    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presented is a mechanically sound E46 M3, powered by the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six featuring six individual throttle bodies and a 8,000 RPM redline. This example has been properly sorted with a reinforced rear subframe and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul, ensuring the valvetrain remains precise and the chassis rigid. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement, while the variable M differential lock ensures optimal torque distribution across the rear axle. Upgraded polyurethane bushings enhance steering rack feedback without compromising the dampening characteristics of the suspension. Though it carries the honest patina of a driver-focused vehicle, its mechanical synchronization and compression across all cylinders remain within tight tolerances.",
      "price": 34500.0,
